query: SELECT bg.id, bg.eventoId, e.tipoEvento, e.turmaId, t.codigo FROM briefing_grupo bg INNER JOIN eventos e ON bg.eventoId = e.id INNER JOIN turmas t ON e.turmaId = t.id LIMIT 20;
